sources, skills, and support to improve their living conditions and enable them to contribute positively to society.\",\"_targets_0_content\":\"field_664cd0d5de3a0\",\"targets_0_theme_color\":\"blue\",\"_targets_0_theme_color\":\"field_664cd0e8de3a1\",\"targets_1_title\":\" UKRAINIAN BUSINESSES (SME)\",\"_targets_1_title\":\"field_664cd0cbde39f\",\"targets_1_content\":\"By accelerating businesses  and helping them to commit to social impact, we contribute to economic recovery and growth.  Strengthening SMEs helps create jobs, fosters innovation, and drives economic stability, which is particularly crucial for Ukraine.\",\"_targets_1_content\":\"field_664cd0d5de3a0\",\"targets_1_theme_color\":\"purple\",\"_targets_1_theme_color\":\"field_664cd0e8de3a1\",\"targets_2_title\":\"GOVERNMENT\",\"_targets_2_title\":\"field_664cd0cbde39f\",\"targets_2_content\":\"Collaborating with government bodies and policymakers is key to ensuring that the needs and challenges identified at the grassroots level are addressed through effective policies and legislation. By advising the government and advocating for policy changes, we help create an enabling environment for our initiatives. This includes reforms that support SME growth, promote gender equality, enhance social inclusion, and align with sustainable development goals.\",\"_targets_2_content\":\"field_664cd0d5de3a0\",\"targets_2_theme_color\":\"green\",\"_targets_2_theme_color\":\"field_664cd0e8de3a1\",\"targets\":3,\"_targets\":\"field_664cd0b8de39e\"},\"mode\":\"edit\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/wwa-team-board {\"name\":\"acf/wwa-team-board\",\"data\":{\"top_row_title\":\"EXECUTIVE BOARD\",\"_top_row_title\":\"field_664cd358253ed\",\"top_row_image\":84,\"_top_row_image\":\"field_664cd363253ee\",\"top_row\":\"\",\"_top_row\":\"field_6647113589219\",\"managers_0_name\":\"Nina Levchuk\",\"_managers_0_name\":\"field_664cd4ae48fea\",\"managers_0_position\":\"Managing Director\",\"_managers_0_position\":\"field_664cd49a48fe8\",\"managers_0_content\":\"\\u003cstrong\\u003e14+\\u003c/strong\\u003e years experience in business development, sales, marketing at Google, SC Johnson and Unilever. Co-founder of Impact Force NGO, United For Ukraine NGO and UA Tech Circle.\",\"_managers_0_content\":\"field_664cd4a448fe9\",\"managers_0_email\":\"nina.levchuk@theimpactforce.org\",\"_managers_0_email\":\"field_664cd4b648feb\",\"managers_0_image\":393,\"_managers_0_image\":\"field_664cd4d948fec\",\"managers_1_name\":\"Olga Diakova\",\"_managers_1_name\":\"field_664cd4ae48fea\",\"managers_1_position\":\"Managing Director\",\"_managers_1_position\":\"field_664cd49a48fe8\",\"managers_1_content\":\"\\u003cstrong\\u003e20-year track record\\u003c/strong\\u003e in driving social behavior change, implementing sustainable business models through organizations like How Women Lead,  the David Lynch Foundation, Slow Food Ukraine, and OII Meaningful Communication.\",\"_managers_1_content\":\"field_664cd4a448fe9\",\"managers_1_email\":\"olga.diakova@theimpactforce.org\",\"_managers_1_email\":\"field_664cd4b648feb\",\"managers_1_image\":394,\"_managers_1_image\":\"field_664cd4d948fec\",\"managers\":2,\"_managers\":\"field_664cd47648fe7\",\"advisors_title\":\"ADVISORY BOARD\",\"_advisors_title\":\"field_664cd83acad89\",\"advisors_slider_0_image\":402,\"_advisors_slider_0_image\":\"field_664cd85acad8b\",\"advisors_slider_0_name\":\"Mathreyi \\u003c/br\\u003e seetharaman\",\"_advisors_slider_0_name\":\"field_664cd867cad8c\",\"advisors_slider_1_image\":403,\"_advisors_slider_1_image\":\"field_664cd85acad8b\",\"advisors_slider_1_name\":\"Ekaterina\\u003c/br\\u003e jalliffier-merlon\",\"_advisors_slider_1_name\":\"field_664cd867cad8c\",\"advisors_slider_2_image\":404,\"_advisors_slider_2_image\":\"field_664cd85acad8b\",\"advisors_slider_2_name\":\"alina\\u003c/br\\u003e nosenko\",\"_advisors_slider_2_name\":\"field_664cd867cad8c\",\"advisors_slider_3_image\":405,\"_advisors_slider_3_image\":\"field_664cd85acad8b\",\"advisors_slider_